    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe `font` argument for `:highlight` command (`:help highlight-font`) is not supported in `nvim_set_hl()`.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n`nvim_set_hl()` should support `font` paramater. GUI fontend such as neovide should support the paramater if notified.",
